The hurricane season in the Caribbean normally runs from June to November. 
Potential Tropical Cyclone Nine, which may develop into a Tropical Storm, is currently forecast to bring hazardous sea and weather conditions to the island from the evening of Wednesday 29 July 2020.
You should monitor local and international weather updates from the World Meteorological Organisation and the National Hurricane Centre.
